<br>
I have tested aggro while drunk (drastic reduction to atk and therefore DPS) and with next to no weapon skill (resulting all hits being either miss or min) and noticed no significant effects either way.  I really don't see how the weapon's actual damage can matter if I can grab aggro while hitting for min on a 2HB weapon with no procs.<br>
<br>
